title: YUMAB partner Enleofen enters joint development Boehringer Ingelheim

meta_description: Enleofen announced collaboration with Boehringer Ingelheim to develop novel anti-IL-11 therapies for a range of fibrotic diseases. YUMAB has been cooperating with Enleofen´s founders – among other partners – to generate an extensive anti-IL-11 platform of fully human antibodies as basis for this next step towards clinical development.
